    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 22.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第22课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "A Glass Envelope.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "玻璃信封。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "How did Jane receive a letter from a stranger?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "简是怎样收到一位陌生人的来信的？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "My daughter, Jane, never dreamed of receiving a letter from a girl of her own age in Holland.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我女儿简做梦也没想到会收到荷兰一位同龄女孩的来信。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "Last year, we were traveling across the channel, and Jane put a piece of paper with her name and address on it into a bottle.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "去年，我们横渡英吉利海峡时，简把写有自己姓名和地址的一张纸装进瓶子里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "She threw the bottle into the sea.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她把瓶子扔进了大海。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "She never thought of it again, but ten months later, she received a letter from a girl in Holland.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她再也没想过这件事，但10个月后，她收到了荷兰一个女孩的来信。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Both girls write to each other regularly now.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "现在两个女孩经常互相通信。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "However, they have decided to use the post office.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "不过，她们决定使用邮局。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "It will cost a little more, but they will certainly travel faster.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这样会多花一点钱，但信肯定会传得更快。"
      }
    }
  ],
